title: Sean Casey & Kevin Millar | Joe Biden Comes Out in Support of Impeaching President Trump
description:
Seth takes a closer look at two of Rudy Giuliani’s associates getting arrested as support for impeachment rises in the polls.

Then, MLB analysts Sean Casey and Kevin Millar talk about their predictions for the MLB post-season, Sean befriending John Cena and Kevin’s rookie hunting mistake. They also take a few bonus questions backstage exclusively for this podcast.
